  "text": "Others have used similar sets of growth factors invariably encompassing combinations of Activin A, Wnt3, bFGF, BMP-4, HGF, Oncostatin M, and/or Dexamethasone (Dex) [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . The number of stages, in which different combinations of growth factors are used, differ somewhat, in various protocols, ranging from three to five.",
